snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP v AMBER HEARD Trial DELAYED Again?
snippet.description:
Is JOHNNY DEPP v AMBER HEARD Trial DELAYED Again? 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_____________________________________________

Johnny Depp had reportedly asked for a US defamation trial against ex-wife Amber Heard to be delayed due to filming commitments. The “Pirates of the Caribbean’’ actor had argued in court papers in the Virginia case that the coronavlrus pushed back the shooting on the latest installment of JK Rowling’s “Fanstastic Beasts’’ movie franchise, creating an “irreconcilable conflict’’ for him with the trial.
